</code></pre></div>
<p>사용자에게서 인증 코드를 받아 검증합니다.</p>
<h3 id='http-request'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>POST /v1/auth/verification/sms</code></p>
<h3 id='scopes'>Scopes</h3>
<ul>
<li><code>user:anonymous</code></li>
</ul>
